{"tid":442072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★又有！有汗出無糧出？　60地盤工天台拉橫額抗議","createTime":"2017-10-20T09:23:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-22T12:03:30.000Z","uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a018718bd5400770d3437291ea03b014014432e8","tid":442072,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T09:23:43.000Z","msg":"尖沙咀有工人抗議欠薪。下午2時許，山林道38號山林大廈天台地盤，近20名工人拉起橫額追討欠薪。其中一名工人黃先生指出，他與近60名工友受聘一間工程公司，負責上址大廈幕牆工程，惟至今仍未收到9月份薪金，涉款逾100萬港元。警方接報到場，勞工處亦派員了解。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171020/bkn-20171020160459375-1020_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171020%2Fbkn-20171020160459375-1020_00822_001.html&d=A7kOZpoo0mE6aRkvZ0BVTU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=63da41e9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171020/bkn-20171020160459375-1020_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8319788a1200270507814ba9b1b6eec17defd0b9","tid":442072,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T09:24:40.000Z","msg":"返工=？"},{"pid":"a291401135a525c4a1161f911d0d48fbca2cfc7d","tid":442072,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T09:25:00.000Z","msg":"人工高<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76789a374e199059fd2a9ef867a353968977993f","tid":442072,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T09:25:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>返工=？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">返工=<img src=\"/assets/face